<p>DESIGN</p>

<ul>
  <li>Task analysis
    <ul>
      <li>“Know thy user”</li>
      <li>“Know thy domain”</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Design principles
    <ul>
      <li>Overarching</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Design guidelines
    <ul>
      <li>Avoid obvious mistakes</li>
      <li>May be vague or contradictory</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

