<p>EVALUATE</p>

<ul>
  <li>Evaluation tests prototypes, using …
    <ul>
      <li>Expert evaluation
        <ul>
          <li>Heuristics and walk-throughs</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Predictive evaluation
        <ul>
          <li>Testing against an engineering model (simulated user)</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Empirical evaluation
        <ul>
          <li>Watching users do it</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

